Batch Script is incorporated to automate command sequences
    Features
        Can read inputs from users
        Has control structures
            for 
            if
            while
            switch
            (..)
        Suport Functions and Arrays
        Regular Expressions
        Can Include Other programming codes such as Perl
    Common users of Batch   
        Setting up servers for different purpoeses
        Automating housekeeping activities such deleting unwanted files or log files
        Automating the deployment of applications from one environment to another
        Installing programs on varios machines at once.
    Extensions for Batch is BAT or CMD
        Recognized and executed through an interface called a shell provided by a system file called Command interpreter
        On Windows system, this interpreter is known as cmd.exe.
